      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：和兌，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, shows the pleasure of (inward) harmony. There will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
