      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 58 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二：孚兌，吉，悔亡。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows the pleasure arising from (inward) sincerity. There will be good fortune. Occasion for repentance will disappear.</seg>
