      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：商兌，未寧，介疾有喜。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows its subject deliberating about what to seek his pleasure in, and not at rest. He borders on what would be injurious, but there will be cause for joy.</seg>
